verbose_text: On the other hand, the addition of lrrc8aa-IRES-eGFP and lrrc8ab-IRES-eGFP mRNA partially and fully rescued the small DMv phenotype resulting from bMO-e2i2, respectively (bMO with a+ + and b+ + mRNA in XREF_FIG A; a+ + : 200 pg, b+ + : 200 pg).
